Mike is right Sid, just loosen the 46mm nut with your big 3/4" socket set, 
and then the hub will slide right off. You can do it, you're well over 6 ft. 
tall, and well over 225 pounds!!! :-)
Courtney


> You need a big socket with a really big handle.  That nut is on there very 
> tight and a puller won't do you any good.  After you remove the nut, the 
> hub will slide right off. 
